{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Occasionally, he would be given some food, some leftovers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would sort of leave it so he could pick up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Any rate, while I was in the-- I could help my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He would come to my-- to the-- to the-- the [CLEARS THROAT] hospital ward.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I would give him-- through the fence, I would give him this bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or you know, he had a special canister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I would give him canisters of soup, and some bread, and some stuff that-- that was easy transported, to-- to be able to give it to him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- [COUGHS] and that camp, the-- we were too-- we were working together with Poles and other nationalities, Italians, civilians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean prisoners, but Polish prisoners, not Jewish, Christians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was a true concentration camp with people from all over the-- the-- in the occupied Reich-- Ukrainians, Ukrainian soldiers, Russian soldiers that escaped and were recaptured.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they would be given-- put into the concentration camp, rather than into POW camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had quite a mixture of people and utilized that period very well to sort of build our strength up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In January of 1945, we were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to go 80 kilometers from Funfteichen to Gross-Rosen, which was further-- [CLEARS THROAT] further west.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the way, the first day, you know, there was-- first of all, I had bread on me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father had bread on him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- when we left, they gave us bread ration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bread disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, people ate it within-- within one day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- it was insane.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you know, when you're very hungry and you have the bread, you eat it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's very difficult to-- to keep it, so-- to save it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
